long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1195251 My CV
Description of problem: After updating LO to 5.2.1.2 my CV's layout was broken and CV was in fact unuseable.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): libreoffice-5.2.1.2-1.fc25.x86_64.rpm
How reproducible: allways
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Open the attached ODT with LO 5.2.1.2-1 2. 3.
Actual results: Layout is broken
Expected results:
Additional info:
Created attachment 1195252 My CV - how it should look like
To fix this, go to "Berufliche". Table->Properties->Text Flow->untick "break"
caolanm->mstahl: this is changed since the referenced commit from justin. Are we happy with this change and just accept it as the new behaviour or do we need to reconsider it ?
i've proposed adding a layout compatibility flag to Justin.
